gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 117, Timberwolves 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pelicans defeated the Timberwolves, 117-106. Zion Williamson recorded 27 points, four rebounds, and six assists for the Pelicans, while CJ McCollum added 24 points (4-6 3PT FG) and five assists in the victory. Anthony Edwards tallied 35 points (4-7 3PT FG) and five assists for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Pelicans have won four consecutive games as they improve to 21-14 on the season, while the Timberwolves fall to 24-9.
